00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:39,820
Scott: But I don't think you would make it as good as it is when you buy it at the store.

575
00:37:40,320 --> 00:37:42,850
Scott: It's just refrigerated there in a plastic container.

576
00:37:43,151 --> 00:37:45,700
Scott: You take it home, you pour it out on top of something.

